===============================================================================
INSERT DATA - Salaries
===============================================================================
Script Purpose:
    This script inserts salary data into the HR Analytics database.
    Includes historical and current compensation data for employees.
    
Prerequisites:
    - Database HRAnalytics must exist
    - Table salaries must be created
